{{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}}
[[File:Zurich Street Parade 2004 002.jpg|thumb|270px|Lovemobile at the 13. Street Parade, 7. August 2004]]

A '''lovemobile''' is a popular name for a [[Float (parade)|float]]. These lovemobiles are trucks with flatbed carrying sound equipment, a [[DJ]] or other live act, [[dancing|dancers]] and props, which is used as a central element at [[technoparade]]s. The setup and decoration of a lovemobile takes place in the days or weeks preceding the event. The lovemobile is driven at walking pace through a crowd of [[rave]]rs as they dance to music powered by the truck's electrical system.

