{{Music-festival-stub}}

The '''Pafos Aphrodite Festival Cyprus''' is a company established to promote [[Paphos]] in [[Cyprus]] as an international centre of high-profile cultural events. Its aim is to organise and manage a yearly international artistic event that takes place at the square in front of the medieval [[Paphos Castle|castle]] at the harbour in Kato Paphos. It organises and hosts an [[opera]] performance at the end of August or early September and has over the years invited a variety of internationally acclaimed companies and performances to the festival:<ref>[http://www.worldeventsguide.com/event/3866/Paphos-Cyprus/Paphos-Aphrodite-Festival-.html Pafos Aphrodite Festival at World Event Guide]</ref>
